      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start for the atmosphere, but it feels a bit generic. I want to get more specific with the \"tension\" part. Can you add some details about some of the people walking around or hanging out on the corners? I want to capture the specific vibe of the crowd in a place like this so the audience knows exactly what kind of neighborhood they're looking at. What would the people look like?",
